Alexa
========
Follow the below instuctions to setup diyHue to work with Alexa.
The Alexa Hue Skill is not required.

1. open devices in the amazon alexa app
2. press "add device"
3. select "other"
4. go to ``http://{IP_ADDRESS}/hue/linkbutton`` and press "acticate"
5. press "Discover devices" in amazon alexa

Alexa will find your lights.
